Within the FurFag community, he is chiefly known for being a [[pedophilia|kiddy fiddler]], sex fiend, and spreader of numerous diseases amongst the UK furries, including Scabies, head lice (many, many times), and Sil-philis, formerly known as [[STD|Syphilis]]. This is particularly due to the fact that he has nothing to offer anyone except for sex, hence his ridiculously bad track record with friends, family, lovers, and anyone else who got bored with the fact that the fetid seed squirted from his engorged and slimy member is the only thing to come from him of any remote interest.

==Recent Drama==

After attending EuroFurence in [[last thursday|Septermber 2009]], Sil decided to Leave The Fandom FOREVAH after fellow furfag, ManicMog told him outright that he wouldn't 'yiff' with him. The drama started to flow when Sil claimed he was "abandoned" by someone at a campfire (when in fact they were indoors puking their faggy guts up with food poisoning and semen overflow). On returning from EF, the rant began with accusations flying in Sil's usual style, (ie not checking facts) and his expected irrational retarded bullshit behaviour.

Needless to say, 1 week later he rejoined the fandom, cruising for cock again, even returning to IRC channel #NorthernFurs from where he was once laughed out, leading to the creation of his own channel, (which it can be assumed isn't going so well... or maybe people there just wont let him interact with their genitals).

Entering into the new decade Sil has decided to try and promote his [[shit|epic new business venture]] with the help of his new [[gullible|friend]] 'Darkus.' "Geeksit" is a company that "helps unpriveledged, living at parents, furs that wish to make something out of their lives" according to the aforementioned bumchum. This raises many questions, though the main one you're probably wondering about is how this epic business is going to make any money? Well with the [[bullshit|amazing marketing skills]] Sil has it won't be a problem for this genius to turn "GeekShit" into a gold mine using a pinch of [[cocksucking|fairy dust]] and a sprinkle of [[attention whore|magic]]! 

Recently, all two of his GeekSit residents just upped and left without so much as a note. Much lulz were had.

